            <title><![CDATA[My Two Cents on Instagram Stories and the Evolution of Social Platform]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<article><h1>My Two Cents on Instagram Stories and the Evolution of Social Platform</h1><p>Yesterday, Instagram, the Facebook-owned photo sharing app, released it's latest platform update: Instagram Stories. It's a new feature that allows you to share photos and videos with your followers in a manner that is incredibly similar to Snapchat. Like Snapchat, this content will disappear after 24 hours.</p><img src="https://imgflo.herokuapp.com/graph/vahj1ThiexotieMo/beed0231443dc0318d65ca101c6ea805/noop.png?input=https%3A%2F%2Fd262ilb51hltx0.cloudfront.net%2Fmax%2F1200%2F1*JAsu6ZSAkONhEDd8IP45PA.png"></article>]]></description>
